The paper discusses security and information management in the context of the Internet of Things, which suggests a focus on computer security (cs.CR) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of smart contracts and blockchain technologies also suggests a focus on distributed computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper discusses the management of information related to Things, which suggests a focus on databases (cs.DB).
